Date: 7-8 October 2020 Location: Inanda Club in Sandton, Johannesburg Website Since its inception, the Joburg Indaba has developed a remarkable reputation as a highly-regarded and influential industry platform which unpacks a wide range of critical issues affecting all stakeholders and thus enjoys overwhelming support from mining and resource companies, investors, labour, government and the media. We are looking forward to welcoming you for more frank, open and honest discussions around the current state of the mining sector and how all stakeholders can work together to move the industry forward